ed="T" n="0834b19"/><persName key="A012443">釋待駕</persName>，俗姓<name>王</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000034875">金水縣</placeName>人也。沖孺出家，作<lb
ed="T" n="0834b20"/>為詭異，其父立名<persName key="A012443"><anchor xml:id="beg0834sgsz14"/>待<anchor xml:id="end0834sgsz14"/>駕</persName>，當<date key="j19960861997410" notBefore-iso="0752" to-iso="0756"><name>天寶</name>末</date>也。練行<lb
ed="T" n="0834b21"/>精進，時號頭陀。及<persName key="A000291">玄宗</persName>巡幸，果自詣府剃<lb
ed="T" n="0834b22"/>䰂<ptr type="glossary" target="#g635"/>為僧。至是「<persName key="A012443">待駕</persName>得度」，其言信矣。<persName key="A012443">駕</persName>去<lb
ed="T" n="0834b23"/>縣邑二十里，開逕芟茅，獨居山頂，後成<placeName key="PL000000037280">一<lb
ed="T" n="0834b24"/>寺</placeName>。此山絕多靈跡，初名<placeName key="PL000000034869">石城</placeName>，迨<persName key="A000291">明皇</persName>至<placeName key="PL000000035738">劍<lb
ed="T" n="0834b25"/>門山</placeName>，神見形迎駕，稱姓李氏，勅賜與玄孫<lb
ed="T" n="0834b26"/>之稱。後陟武擔東臺，遠望祥雲紫氣，盤結<lb
ed="T" n="0834b27"/>空界，問左右曰：「此何處？」對曰：「名城山。」乃悟<lb
ed="T" n="0834b28"/>山神扈衛之意，遂改<placeName key="PL000000037280">雲頂</placeName>為<placeName key="PL000000037280">慈雲寺</placeName>也。<persName key="A012443">駕</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0834b29"/>後卒<anchor xml:id="beg0834sgsz16"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>干</sic><corr>于</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0834sgsz16"/><placeName key="PL000000037280">此寺</placeName>。又福州<placeName key="PL000000017146">楞伽寺</placeName><persName key="A010861">釋懷一</persName>，<date key="j19795671980570" notBefore-iso="+0707-10-09" notAfter-iso="+0710-07-08"><name>景龍</name>中</date><pb ed="T" n="0834c" xml:id="T50.2061.0834c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0834c01"/>銳意於<placeName key="PL000000017197">愛同寺</placeName>東造精舍，相度地形，無水<lb
ed="T" n="0834c02"/>濟用，方拱手而去。忽山禽擊鬪於地，<persName key="A010861">一</persName>異<lb
ed="T" n="0834c03"/>之，命工穴深尺餘，甘泉沸湧。此後伏臘而<lb
ed="T" n="0834c04"/>無加耗。寺中每有休咎，必暫減耗，候以知<lb
ed="T" n="0834c05"/>之，風俗謂之靈泉焉。以<date key="j20008842001190" notBefore-iso="0766-02-18" to-iso="0766-12-21"><name>永泰</name>二年</date>歸寂，弟<lb
ed="T" n="0834c06"/>子<persName key="A012450">超悟</persName>奏乞<persName key="A004379">代宗</persName>題寺額。上首曰<persName key="A012453">智恒</persName>，次<lb
ed="T" n="0834c07"/><persName key="A012451">行<anchor xml:id="beg0834sgsz18"/>弼<anchor xml:id="end0834sgsz18"/></persName>。<placeName key="PL000000013239">越州</placeName><anchor xml:id="begd1e34292"/>刺<anchor xml:id="endd1e34292"/>史<persName key="A012449">皇甫政</persName>為碑紀德，<placeName key="PL000000027118">襄州</placeName>節<lb
ed="T" n="0834c08"/>度使<persName key="A000047">于頔</persName>書焉。</p>
